# WebSocket server URL
# For local development, leave empty (defaults to ws://localhost:3002)
# For Cloudflare tunnel testing, set to your tunnel URL:
#   VITE_WS_URL=wss://your-server-tunnel.trycloudflare.com
# For the production Yandex Games build, point at the deployed server:
#   VITE_WS_URL=wss://street-dice.online/ws
# When this is empty the Yandex build runs as an offline solo-only build
# (no Multiplayer menu item, no signed-data network calls).
VITE_WS_URL=

# Build platform selector (used by vite.config.ts).
# Leave unset for the canonical Telegram build. Set to `yandex` to produce
# the Yandex Games build (different entry HTML, wsClient alias, etc.). The
# `npm run build:yandex` script already sets this for you.
# VITE_PLATFORM=yandex
